Class FileParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.sw.Parser

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileToShingleParser

    public class FileParser
extends Parser
    FileParser class extends from the abstract class Parser implementing its parse method. Provides the functionality of the buffered reading of an input stream. Input is stripped of punctuation and converted to lowercase for processing.
    Author:
    Daire Ní Chatháin
